pe":"heading"},{"data":{"text":"Introduction"},"id":"605ca42d-4d5f-4b2d-8cbf-99ebfaee637f","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["<em>Editor&#39;s Note: This review has been removed from our side-by-side comparison because it no longer ranks as a top 10 product. The original review is below, but check out our current top 10 </em><em><a href=\"/best-programmable-thermostats\">Programmable Thermostat</a> products</em><em>.</em>","Honeywell products are a mainstay in the home comfort game, and the RTH8500D programmable thermostat is no exception. It has a large touchscreen, which makes for easy programming. This home thermostat also permanently holds dates you put in, even during power outages. While this unit has some standout features, its ability to work with only single-stage heating and cooling limits its compatibility somewhat.","The 8500D comes standard with all of the Honeywell features that make programming easy. This programmable thermostat has seven-day scheduling with the option to set four different schedules each day. Smart response technology senses what temperature you want and will reach target temperature at the time you schedule it to. So, if you wake up at 7 a.m. and want the temperature to be 70 degrees when you wake up, the 8500D will start the air so it reaches the desired temperature when you get out of bed.","You can override any current schedules on the thermostat with the push of one button or change the programming from automatic to manual if you are home during times you normally aren&#39;t. This is especially useful for anyone whose schedule is constantly changing.","The do-it-yourself installation is easy with the built-in level. The only setback when installing this device is it only works with single-stage AC and heating units. If you don&#39;t know how many stages your unit has, HVAC companies will send a technician and inform you what kind of thermostat you need. The thermostat is also missing a humidity sensor and outdoor temperature display, but these upgrades aren&#39;t essential to a comfortable home.","There are plenty of other solid features on the 8500D thermostat. This device tells you when it&#39;s time to change the air filter and informs you of any malfunctions with your AC or heating unit. You can also program the fan to turn on and ventilate your home while you are away.","The Honeywell RTH8500D comes with a five-year, registered warranty. Honeywell&#39;s website has a huge support section with installation videos and demos as well as documents for installing and programming your digital thermostat."]},"id":"b555f58f-d7ff-4ea8-92de-2d1edb73b34b","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"0d523675-b321-4f6e-b5da-fdc2891bebc1","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["Single-stage heating and cooling make this programmable thermostat fall a little short when compared with similar units, but this smart thermostat is equipped with seven-day programming and helps you maintain your HVAC units – a great feature. Using a RTH8500D thermostat from Honeywell ensures that your home will stay comfortable, no matter what season it is."]},"id":"c46238d3-43c2-4681-9591-76d946244461","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_54843","url":"/honeywell-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"john-carlsen","url":"/author/john-carlsen","dateCreated":"2019-04-05T10:05:21Z","name":"John Carlsen","dateModified":"2019-04-05T10:05:21Z","id":"jN6fuw55cS2xYQi25mfgkg","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2012-06-21T12:54:55Z","datePublished":"2012-06-21T12:54:55Z","name":"Honeywell RTH8500D","synopsis":"Editor's Note: This review has been removed from our side-by-side comparison because it no longer ranks as a top 10 product.","review":{"rating":62,"verdict":"Easy seven-day programming makes the RTH8500D perfect for someone with a regular week-to-week schedule.","pros":["The Smart Response technology will make sure the temp